Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.72,0:28:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yeah. How do you not revert?\N>> Revert
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.91,0:28:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,>> and become a reverter.\N>> We don't allow reverters in this
