Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.00,0:29:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,each other uh you know look of a glance\Nof love and it would just wipe me out
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.36,0:29:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and tears would come up and I just shot\Nthe bliss state you know you get to be
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.88,0:29:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,mother so and so you just sit there in a\Nstate of bliss and you can't really say
