Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.40,0:40:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and hopefully up the evolutionary tree\Nand um
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.24,0:40:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,all right so then we'd say that every\Nact of the will every uh ascent of the
