Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.11,0:41:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Um but it's an extremelyformational\Ntool. Extremelyformational.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.07,0:41:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,pretty much like a compass, you know,\Nand to navigate without a compass is
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.80,0:41:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,where mankind has been. Mankind has been\Nunable to know truth from falsehood.
