Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.44,1:02:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say you discover somebody does a\Nlot of money from you and you want to
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.11,1:02:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,get even.\NWell,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.55,1:02:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it helps to find out that karmically you\Nembezzled a lot out of a lot of people,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.28,1:02:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of lifetimes and it's payback\Ntime. That makes a lot little easier to
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.04,1:02:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,handle right there. Yeah.\NAnd to see that it doesn't really
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.59,1:02:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,matter. So the willingness to let every\Ninstant be the past of course closes the
