Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.72,1:02:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,means like listening to music to let go\Nof the last note
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.79,1:03:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and make room for the next. So each\Nthing as it arises, you can let go
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.40,1:03:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,wanting to change it. And with the\Nwillingness to surrender this instant to
