Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.75,1:09:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you begin to trust your own\Nspiritual inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.88,1:09:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,See the presence of God within you\Nexpresses itself as spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.64,1:09:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,inspiration which is what leads you into\Nspiritual pathways and attending
