Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.31,1:09:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not personal. So you can't\Ncompliment yourself that you're
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.52,1:09:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritually oriented nor can you attack\Nyourself that you aren't.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.15,1:09:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness itself is impersonal.\NEverybody has it. Awareness is
